name: Sadness
description:
When I was child, I was the victim of bullying from my school friends. I grew up with insecure feelings. 

I feel different (in a less good way). Until now, several times I feel very insecure in many ways and feel lonely, even though there are many people around me.

I pour this feeling into a photo to treat my loneliness.

*the file is corrupt and cannot be perfect.
